<br>
I have already long since justfied it to myself.  I have been happier with the decision as time has gone by.  After I have bought all the AA skills I want, my friends are all in PoP zones too, and I have enough of the PoP spells waiting for me in the bank I will not level.<br>
<br>
The times I have gotten bored of soloing, group up with some guildies, or go on a raid, or just head over to PoP zones and look for groups.  I really don't see how remaining 60 has in any way decreased my grouping ability.  But dinging to 65 will indeed decrease my solo ability. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Master Eandori Raintree<br>
